{"tid":2089782,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"亞裔留學生受歧視 英國倫敦街頭被毆打","createTime":"2020-07-01T23:45:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T23:54:50.000Z","uid":52215,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5fe0fda13fb296ad0b4e95113af1ca0870369469","tid":2089782,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T23:45:45.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎：亞裔留學生受歧視 倫敦街頭被毆打<br />\n<br />\n一名新加坡留學生2月24日在英國倫敦街頭被人襲擊，面部受傷嚴重。倫敦警察廳表示，該案件帶有種族主義特性。<br />\n<br />\n受害者是倫敦大學學院法律系的學生莫顯強，現年24歲。<br />\n<br />\n他回憶，施襲者在施暴前曾大叫：「我不想你把新冠病毒帶來我的國家」。"},{"pid":"bfce74ca30b2a0ba2da0281d71949503fe10a96a","tid":2089782,"uid":180703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T23:50:55.000Z","msg":"lol"},{"pid":"017234bea99ba143649df69ec0b249d04e2a445b","tid":2089782,"uid":263261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T23:54:50.000Z","msg":"雖然係monkey<br />\n但都係抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}